description:
These methodological annexes correspond to the development of the research document  Gender Digital Divides: New Divides, Old Inequalities  and are composed of three documents: Systematic review that contains the search equation and the number of documents obtained in the databases used and the selection of the sample according to the Proknow-C methodology, PRISMA protocol and CASP checklist. 
 It also contains the 90 selected documents with the review tables and the inclusion criteria according to the PRISMA protocol and CASP checklist. 
 &nbsp;

